DeployProxy:
name             Deploy proxy server on Windows Clients
description      The proxy server will set with a registry patch on each Windows Login.\nFurthermore the Connection Tab in the Internet Options of Windows will be hidden with a entry in the IServ Windows Registry Patch. The Firefox Package in the Software Deployment will configured to use the proxy server which is configured in iservcfg. 
group            Module: Proxy Configuration
type             bool
default          false

DeployProxyUse:
name             Proxy server to deploy
description      The proxy server which will deployed to the Windows Clients.\nempty: Use configuration of IServ (Proxy in iservcfg). direct: Configure Windows to use a direct internet connection. auto: Try to configure Windows to use WPAD/PAC. script: Use the PAC script of IServ. other: Proxy server in format hostname:port. 
group            Module: Proxy Configuration
type             string
default          auto

ProxyDMZMode:
name             Enable DMZ mode (Hamburg)
description      The Firewall of the IServ will configured to allow access to the proxy from another subnets.\nEnable this to allow the access to the Proxy if the IServ is homed in a DMZ of a Time for kids-Schulrouter.
group            Module: Proxy Configuration
type             bool
default          false

ProxyCacheMgr:
name             Squid Webmaster
description      E-Mail Address which is shown as Cache Administrator on Squid error pages
group            Module: Proxy Configuration
type             string
default          webmaster

ProxyCachePeer:
name             Cache Peer
description      Proxy server to which all requests are redirected by the IServ Proxy.\nProxy server in format hostname:port
group            Module: Proxy Configuration
type             string

TrustedChildProxies:
name             Trusted Child Proxies
description      Child Proxies where the field 'X-Forwarded-For' is trusted. It will used to detect the origin of a request.
group            Module: Proxy Configuration
type             array
default          ()
